T1  - A Multiproduct Inventory System with Interactive Set-Up Costs
AU  - Andres, Fred
AU  - Emmons, Hamilton
Y1  - 1975/05/01
PY  - 1975
DA  - 1975/05/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.21.9.1055
