N2  - Heuristic decision rules for the s, S policy in probabilistic inventory systems are proposed. The rules require only the knowledge of the mean and standard deviation of demand, probability of no demand, carrying and replenishing costs, desired availability, and leadtime. Numerical results are given to illustrate the application of the rules.
